
You fight to kill monsters. You can either use magic or weapons.

To use weapons, simply wield a weapon (and armor!) and move into the monster you want to attack.

To use magic or bows, read
    'help spells
and
    'help range
and
    'help cast
and
    'help invoke

See Also: [help]spells[/help]
See Also: [help]range[/help]
See Also: [help]cast[/help]
See Also: [help]invoke[/help]
